OL,3,CConvicted stalker shot in neck and
OL,4,Cchest by police in south London,
OL,5,Cinquest told
OL,7,FA man was shot in the neck and chest
OL,8,Fby police, an inquest has heard.
OL,10,FConvicted stalker Bryce Hodgson was
OL,11,Fshot dead by armed officers on January
OL,12,F30 this year after he broke into a
OL,13,Fhome in Bywater Place, Surrey Quays,
OL,14,Fsouth-east London.
OL,16,FThe inquest into the 30-year-old's
OL,17,Fdeath was opened on Wednesday at
OL,18,FSouthwark Coroner's Court, which heard
OL,19,Fthat Hodgson had gained entrance to
OL,20,Fthe property armed with a crossbow and
OL,21,Fother weapons.
