OL,7,FSenior Coroner Dr Julian Morris said:
OL,8,F"He had entered Bywater Place armed
OL,9,Fwith various weapons, including a
OL,10,Fcrossbow.
OL,12,F"Police were called to the scene and,
OL,13,Fwhen he exhibited some threatening
OL,14,Fbehaviour, armed response units were
OL,15,Fcalled and subsequently shots were
OL,16,Ffired.
OL,18,F"He was pronounced dead at the scene."
