OL,7,FA provisional post-mortem examination
OL,8,Freport found Hodgson died from gunshot
OL,9,Fwounds to his neck and chest.
OL,11,FThe Independent Office of Police
OL,12,FConduct (IOPC) is currently
OL,13,Finvestigating the incident and Harriet
OL,14,FGriffiths, lead investigator on the
OL,15,Fcase, said: "Police units attended but
OL,16,Fwere unable to detain him and they
OL,17,Fwere shortly followed by their
OL,18,Ffirearms colleagues, who, as you know,
OL,19,Ffired shots."
