OL,7,FThe inquest heard that Hodgson, from
OL,8,FSheffield, was single and working in
OL,9,FIT at the time of his death, and his
OL,10,Flast known address was in south-east
OL,11,FLondon.
OL,13,FThe hearing was adjourned for the IOPC
OL,14,Fto continue its investigation.
